Package Server

Class Summary
ChatServer Description of ChatServer: This class is called ChatServer and it creates a ServerSocket that is related to the chat where messages get sent through a list.
EditorServer Description of EditorServer: This class creates a EditorServer that contains a ServerSocket called "CollaborativeSocket", this is the server that sends all the collabrative things that users can do together.
PaintServer Description of PaintServer: This class is called PaintServer and it is the server where the paint commands communicates.
Run_To_Start_Servers Description of Run_To_Start_Servers: This is what runs the servers and starts their commands.
